Package: ggerror
Title: A lightweight wrapper around ggplot2's error geoms. designed for simplicity & flexibility.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yann", "Cohen", , "yannco5@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-0509-3609"))
Description: Provides a single geom layer, geom_error(), that wraps
    ggplot2 error bar geoms with automatic orientation inference. Users
    declare an error aesthetic and the package computes the min/max bounds
    and dispatches to geom_errorbar(), geom_linerange(), geom_crossbar(),
    or geom_pointrange().
